  m_Text: "TERMS OF USE\r\nVersion April 2023\r\n\r\nDont Play to Game In Restricted
    Area Like Andhrapradesh, Telangna,Tamilnadu,Odisa,Assam,Sikkim,Nagaland etc if
    play there company not will be responssibale.\r\nWelcome to Game Winner Infotech
    App We (Game Winner Infotech App, a company established in the India - hereafter
    referred to as 'Game Winner Infotech App', 'we', 'our' or 'us') operate a website,
    accessible at https://poki.com. In this document we explainthe terms of use for
    our Game Winner Infotech App. Please click this link for an overview of the domains
    referred to as \u201C Game Winner Infotech \u201D. The Game Winner Infotech Website
    may include access to virtual environments, games and other content, as well
    as downloadable software or applications for use on personal computers, tablets,
    mobile devices or phones. All users of the Game Winner Infotech Website (\u201CWebsite
    Visitors\u201D) are subject to the following terms and conditions of use (these
    \u201CTerms of Use\u201D).\r\n\r\nPlease read these Terms of Use carefully before
    accessing or using any part of this Game Winner Infotech App. By accessing or
    using this Game Winner Infotech App, you agree that you have read, understand
    and agree to be bound by these Terms of Use, as amended from time to time by
    Game Winner Infotech . If you do not wish to agree to these Terms of Use, do
    not access or use any part of this Game Winner Infotech Website.\r\n\r\nGame
    Winner Infotech App may revise and update these Terms of Use at any and if we
    do so, we will notify you by posting the revised Terms of Use on the Game Winner
    Infotech App\r\n1. Age\r\nBy accessing the Game Winner Infotech App, you attest
    that you are 18 years of age or older. If you are younger than 18 years. Use
    of this website\r\nYou agree to use the Site only for lawful purposes:\r\n\r\n(a)
    Specifically you agree not to do any of the following: (1) upload to or transmit
    on the Game Winner Infotech App any defamatory, indecent, obscene, harassing,
    violent or otherwise objectionable material, or any material that is, or may
    be, protected by copyright, without permission from the copyright owner; (2)
    use the Game Winner Infotech App to violate the legal rights (including the rights
    of publicity and privacy) of others or to violate the laws of any jurisdiction;
    (3) intercept or attempt to intercept electronic mail not intended for you; (4)
    misrepresent an affiliation with any person or organization; (5) upload to or
    transmit on the Game Winner Infotech App any advertisements or solicitations
    of business; (6) restrict or inhibit use of the Game Winner Infotech App by others;
    (7) upload or otherwise transmit files that contain a virus or corrupted data;
    (8) collect information about others (including e-mail addresses) without their
    consent; (9) download a file or software or include in a message any software,
    files or links that you know, or have reason to believe, cannot be distributed
    legally over the Game Winner Infotech App or that you have a contractual obligation
    to keep confidential (notwithstanding its availability on the Game Winner Infotech
    App); (10) post \u201Cspam,\u201D transmit chain letters or engage in other similar
    activities; (11) solicit, provide or exchange any personal information, including
    but not limited to user names or passwords; (12) \u201Cstalk,\u201D \u201Cphish,\u201D
    abuse or harass another user, or attempt to do any of the foregoing; or (13)
    engage in any other conduct that restricts or inhibits anyone's use or enjoyment
    of the Game Winner Infotech App, or which, as determined by Game Winner Infotech
    App, may harm Game Winner Infotech App or Website Visitors or expose them to
    liability. Without limiting any of the foregoing, you also agree to abide by
    any code of conduct and policies applicable to the Game Winner Infotech App or
    any service available on the Game Winner Infotech App.\r\n\r\n(b) Any content
    and/or opinions uploaded, expressed or submitted to a message board, blog, chatroom
    or any other publicly available section of the Game Winner Infotech App(including
    password-protected areas), and all articles and responses to questions, other
    than the content provided by Game Winner Infotech App, are solely the opinions
    and responsibility of the person or entity submitting them and do not necessarily
    reflect the opinions of Game Winner Infotech App. You understand and acknowledge
    that you are responsible for whatever content you submit, and you, notGame Winner
    Infotech App, have full responsibility for such content, including its legality,
    reliability and appropriateness. By uploading or otherwise transmitting material
    to any area of the Poki Website, you warrant that the material is your own or
    is in the public domain or otherwise free of proprietary or other restrictions
    and that you have the right to post it to the Game Winner Infotech App. You grant
