    App chooses, including, but not limited, to copying, displaying, performing or
    publishing it in any format or media whatsoever, modifying it, incorporating
    it into other material or making a derivative work based on it.\r\n\r\n(c) Except
    as expressly authorized by Game Winner Infotech App in writing, you may not reproduce,
    sublicense, distribute, sell or exploit for any commercial purposes (i) any part
    of this Game Winner Infotech App or its content, (ii) access to this Game Winner
