    Infotech App or any Game Winner Infotech App applications will be compatible
    with any updates to, or prior versions of, your devices.Game Winner Infotech
    App may, but is not obligated to, provide you with updates to the Game Winner
    Infotech App or applications that improve compatibility with updated mobile devic\r\n6.
    Copyright restrictions/use of content\r\nThe entire contents of this Game Winner
    Infotech App (including all information, text, displays, images and audio and
    any software made available through or in connection with the Game Winner Infotech
