    (b) store files that are automatically cached by your web browser for display
    enhancement purposes, and (c) print a reasonable number of pages of the Game
    Winner Infotech App; provided in each case that you do not alter or remove any
    copyright or other proprietary notices included in such materials. Neither the
    title nor any intellectual property rights to any information or material in
    this Game Winner Infotech App are transferred to you, but remain with Game Winner
    Infotech App or the applicable owner of such content.\r\n17. Miscellaneous\r\nThese
    Terms of Use, as they may be amended from time to time, completely and exclusively
    state the agreement between you andGame Winner Infotech App with respect to the
    Game Winner Infotech App, and no other terms that may have been communicated
